{"categories":["newsletter","fashion"],"collections":"","description":"Step into a world of style with this chic email template, perfect for sharing the latest trends and updates in fashion and lifestyle. Its two-column layout offers a clean and organized space to effectively communicate your content. The template is designed with an elegant serif typography, adding a touch of sophistication to your messages. The striking use of red against a light white background captures attention and stirs interest, ensuring your newsletters stand out in your subscribers' inbox. This template is not merely a communication tool but a fashion statement on its own, allowing you to connect with your audience in a stylish and engaging manner. Ideal for fashion bloggers, lifestyle brands, and style influencers looking to share their love for fashion with their followers.","short_description":"Discover style with this chic email template, ideal for fashion and lifestyle updates. It boasts a two-column layout, elegant serif typography, and a striking red and white palette. Communicate effectively, engage your audience, and make a fashion statement. Perfect for fashion bloggers and lifestyle brands.","designer":{"avatar_url":"https://d1oco4z2z1fhwp.cloudfront.net/designers/Beefree_TemplateCatalog_ProfileImage_400x400_1.png","description":"A team of passionate designers, marketers, and technologists with an understanding that great design inspires action. At Beefree, we’re committed to creating responsive, mobile-friendly, and high-converting templates that empower teams to get more done with less time.","short_description":"","display_name":"Beefree Team","id":"beefree-team"},"html_data":"<!DOCTYPE html><html xmlns:v=\"urn:schemas-microsoft-com:vml\" xmlns:o=\"urn:schemas-microsoft-com:office:office\" lang=\"en\"><head><title></title><meta http-equiv=\"Content-Type\" content=\"text/html; charset=utf-8\"><meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width,initial-scale=1\"><!--[if mso]><